Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————正文——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然想抗拒我的指示  當初可不是這樣說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吾意已決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不再退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不再獻媚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不再多慮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,吾將與你抗爭到底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢  你應該也還沒忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,關於{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}人質{\r}的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊…什麼人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…大神同學是…{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}內奸{\r}？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,第三次學級裁判結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們開始著手調查新開放的{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}校舍4樓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都這個時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,十神同學和腐川同學能一起來的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？苗木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在4樓發現的有{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}職員室{\r}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還有{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}化學室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看  超{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}高級蛋白質「蛋白伴侶X」{\r}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點  朝日奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊都是毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,另外還有{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}音樂室{\r}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}情報處理室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,門被鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最後是{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}校長室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也鎖上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,苗木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,霧切同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你過來下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,之前說的那間暗房  後來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛要開始調查的時候  就被什麼人襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等我再醒過來的時候  資料已經都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我在那間房間裡發現了一張奇怪的便條
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事最好不要現在在這裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  苗木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼事瞞著我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,瞞著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學有可能是內奸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還沒有確鑿證據就這麼說了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不能說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前對我說過這樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴就要互相信任  知無不言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,結果什麼都沒發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是情報處理室和校長室裡說不定有什麼線索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那鎖要是可以打開的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直接把門撞開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事對最強靈長類動物的大神來說還不是小菜一碟噠唄！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然想要打破校長室的門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你們玩的到底是什麼「School Wars」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我本並不想用校規束縛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,又加了條…校規…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,唔噗噗  這樣就可以放心了  回頭見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜做到這個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說校長室和情報處理室裡果然有著些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,對…對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不還有「那個」嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,「Alter Ego」呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,文件的解密終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！幹得好唄！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.60,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  這所學校似乎正在進行著{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}某項計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在希望峰學園裡把學生們隔離起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,並讓他們開始共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且被隔離的高中生們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能需要一輩子都在學校裡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是吾等如今所處之境況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且似乎提出這個計劃的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}希望峰學園本身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是學校的意思…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而學校之所以制定了這個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為1年前發生的{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}「人類史上最大最惡劣的絕望事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,「人類史上最大最惡劣的絕望事件」…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個事件  希望峰學園也被迫閉校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,並啟動了隔離計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,計劃的負責人是希望峰學園的{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}校長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一名將近40歲的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現在很有可能仍在學校之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說是這個校長操縱著黑白熊了噠唄！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,校長…就由我來把他找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我…一定會把他找出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,霧切同學…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我從數據裡還發現了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,又是謎一般的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這照片是怎麼回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,校內廣播  校內廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,請立刻到體育館集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還是去一下比較好吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}緊急  緊急  緊急  緊急！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要通知你們一個悲傷的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你們中出了一個內奸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,內…內奸…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,果然和我預想的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,誰  是誰  誰是內奸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,唔噗噗噗…別急我會告訴你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這個內奸就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大神櫻同學！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大…大神是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,內奸…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,唔噗噗…接下來就隨你們的便了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是煮是烤  是殺還是被殺  啊哈哈哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小…櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一直瞞著大家…實在是抱歉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你真…真的是黑幕的手下嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都在騙我們嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻肯定只是被迫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯！我都看見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學和黑白熊對峙的場景…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候黑白熊說了「人質」什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學因為人質的關係而被脅迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在已經背叛黑幕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}真是蠢得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是活在童話世界裡的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  如果你真的背叛了黑幕  那就回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,黑幕究竟是何方神聖？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…這個吾也毫不知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哼…那就更奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  黑幕又給過你什麼樣的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在學校之中沒有發生殺人事件  陷入膠著狀態的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓我去殺一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以即使是現在  其實我們的小命也都在你手上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,事已至此  也沒有必要再為吾之問題而爭論了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,責任皆在於吾一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日奈啊  抱歉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你…吾曾經好幾次都猶豫著是不是要向你坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然而吾還是害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕會被你討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼會…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何即使事與願違我也要負起這份責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,事與願違…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看來今後最好還是要多多當心大神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,十神同學  你這種說法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不…其實十神親說的也對噠唄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是黑幕的人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼就不能理解小櫻呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是  對於那個傢伙的事你又究竟瞭解多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也根本不知道關於她的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要是大神能把黑幕幹掉的話  那就還是可以相信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一出了什麼事怎麼辦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哼…就算大神死了  那也只是說黑幕那邊的人少了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,又有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你才應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼…真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就來殺我試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,動手吧  這就是這裡的規則吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得…我下不了手是吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你這頭母豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢這樣對白夜大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直就該千刀萬剮！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再這麼吵下去  那就是正中黑幕下懷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去…回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,十神同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是相當輕視別人的情感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就給你個忠告  這樣的話你總有一天要馬失前蹄的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,萬分感謝您的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…校內廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,已經是晚上10點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,現在進入夜間時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,腐川和朝日奈…爭執了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的不可萌男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快點把這女人帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的話  剪碎剪碎剪碎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要解放享受這快感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日奈同學  總之先去保健室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,葉隱同學  你來幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  只是點擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是我大聲喊叫的話  你就被殺掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可要謝我唄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那還真是太感謝了  還請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日奈同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}我怎麼從你的話裡感覺到了敵意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟腐川同學之間發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為小櫻的事稍微吵了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為  因為最重要的朋友被人說壞話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日奈  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這傷是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼大不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是我拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,滅族者唄  是那個變態殺人狂幹的唄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然不是我…而是朝日奈受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太過分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16}救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}不能原諒  不能原諒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大…大神同學  冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在吵些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,霧切同學也來幫忙阻止大神同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有必要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只是去做個了斷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…你還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是在生氣吧  是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,苗木同學隱瞞的是大神同學的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓不確切的情報使大家產生混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才瞞著我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種事上為我們著想  苗木同學什麼時候也這麼自大起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你歸根結底還是沒有信任過我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事  我會忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我也稍微有點生氣過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個  Alter Ego好像有什麼事要告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然由Alter Ego叫我們過來  到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  希望你們能把我帶到可以連接到網絡的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,讓大家能從這座學園裡逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  要讓我為大家做些什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,必須先讓我連接上網絡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我還是必須要這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  一想到大家我就充滿了勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可能會想明明是人工智能卻在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但這都是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,苗木同學  我們將他連接到網絡上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想體諒一下他的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,霧切同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而且說不定  放在那裡的話可能不會被黑幕所發現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,二樓的密室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那個房間也沒有監視攝像頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也有網絡環境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也不能保證黑幕沒有干涉網路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還是有嘗試一下的價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  那麼我就把Alter Ego搬過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  看來行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就交給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會找到線索的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就相信我  等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也算是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  苗木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,超高校級的格鬥家（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,密室殺人（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我發現了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,括號的偉大之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎麼消極的話語  加上了（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就會變得很積極
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼現在倖存的學生還有七名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還會再減少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的我能做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的我能做的就只有相信同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,苗木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,門打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學  快把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就一直沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,門上鎖了  或者是門後有什麼東西擋著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  到底該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大神同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叮咚咚咚　發現屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在一定的自由時間後將舉行{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}學級裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事又發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人…小櫻她…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家…必須把大家都叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日奈同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的…我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,遺體頭部有兩處{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}擊打痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從口中有{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}吐血跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,腳背上有{\c&H12BEFA&\3c&H115686&}粉末{\r}附著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,霧切同學真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了多少遍都沒辦法習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是從以前就經常像這樣接觸屍體…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 　現場的門是從內側鎖住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是密室殺人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,密室殺人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,門被鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,犯人是怎麼將大神同學…殺害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　大…大神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀　這看起來是死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你們聽到發現屍體的廣播了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,十神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,葉隱　腐川
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死小櫻的　就是你們當中的某個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會這麼認為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻把這三個人叫到了娛樂室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,最後見到小櫻的犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你們三個人當中的某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,唔呼呼呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————OPCN——————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}現實{\r}離我們遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}虛幻{\r}來臨  成為其中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,緊閉的大門之後{\c&H2208CF&}希望{\r}不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,漸漸遠離原先的所在之處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}希望和絕望{\r}成為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,一切都是{\c&H2208CF&}浮雲{\r}  遊戲已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,是的  我們是一夥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,從來不是對手  有著一致的{\c&H2208CF&}目標{\r}的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們遊走在{\c&H2208CF&}希望和絕望{\r}的鋼絲上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,試圖{\c&H2208CF&}逃避現實{\r}但它已呈現於此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}謊言連篇{\r}  我不知自己是否能被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:15.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}生命{\r}只有一次  所以要做出明智選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}正面{\r}還是{\c&H2208CF&}反面{\r}  你還知道自己站在哪一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,其實無所謂正反  只要是在同一硬幣上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,如果你想要成功你就得{\c&H2208CF&}堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在是時候了 那裡是門 這是打開的{\c&H2208CF&}鑰匙{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,只是要把痛苦帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,讓它消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,絕望的背後留存了一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,前進吧 探索這個世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,只有一次努力掙扎的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,突破困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,尋找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,戰勝那些扭曲的邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,想做就做吧 行動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,你要相信殺戮時刻已經來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————OPEN——————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Reality{\r} slips far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Fiction{\r} comes alive as start to play
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:57.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Hope{\r} is no more behind a closed door
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,As we drift away from what was once before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Hope and hopelessness{\r} become one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,It's all {\c&H2208CF&}meaningless{\r} we've already begun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,we are all one in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Never opposites when we play the same {\c&H2208CF&}game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,We walk a thin line between {\c&H2208CF&}hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Running from the {\c&H2208CF&}truth{\r} but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Told so many {\c&H2208CF&}lies{\r} I don't know if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:15.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Only one {\c&H2208CF&}life{\r} to live so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2208CF&}Heads{\r} or {\c&H2208CF&}tails{\r}? do you know what side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Does it even matter if it's on the same coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,If you wanna achieve you gotta {\c&H2208CF&}believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,The time is right now there's the door here's the {\c&H2208CF&}keys{\r}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Just gotta chase the pain away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,let it fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,There's a ray of hope beyond despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Move on look for the truth in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Such dedication comes through only once
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Break through the confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Beat the twisted evil things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Just do it, go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\c&H2208CF&}Never
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,You gotta believe it's killin' time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————EDJP——————————
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}「君の望む物はなに？」耳鳴り  嘘みたいな話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:23.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}どうやらボクの世界はバグってしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:28.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}遮る煩悩  ソイツが言うには等価交換だと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:32.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}誘惑従い戯れ言に溺れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}王様ゲーム強制参加
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}拒否権なんて聴いちゃくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:41.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}課せられたクエストには「あのモブを殺せ」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}絶望ダンス  野望塗れ少年に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:46.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}逃げ込んだ現実  嗤った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}欲望ないとか偽り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}偽善者ぶってもしかたないや
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}憧れた夢なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}『ヒーローになりたいの？（笑）』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(22.333,253.334)}{\fs6\pos(381,3)}ウププ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}願い口にする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:02.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(35,176)}「生憎馬鹿につける薬はないよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————EDCN——————————
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}「你的願望是什麼？」耳鳴似的話語  仿佛謊言一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:23.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}看來我的世界出現了Bug
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:28.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}擾人的煩惱  以它的話說便是等價交換
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:32.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}我沒有經得住誘惑沉浸在它的玩笑之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}國王遊戲強制參加
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}根本不容我拒絕的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:41.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}接到的任務居然是「殺了那個路人」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}絕望的Dance  在胸懷野心的少年面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:46.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}被逃避的現實放聲大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}無慾無求只是虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}裝成偽善者的樣子也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}你憧憬的夢想是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}『不是成為英雄嗎？（笑）』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(616,234)}{\fs9}唔噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}而當我說出願望的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:02.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\frz-90\pos(605,176)}「很遺憾笨蛋是沒有藥醫的」
